All right. man.
Then how much 10Gs get you in here. huh?

71
00:04:50.707 --> 00:04:54.377
What it get you? It-It gets you what.
Big Macs? Uzi's? Street sweepers?

72
00:04:54.378 --> 00:04:55.628
